tps://reader.miniflux. 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"/></picture></a></figure><p>NYU Computer Scientist Mengye Ren explained what was going on. Guess what? It’s the same issue of canonical versus noncanonical statistics, all over again.</p><figure><a href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F00b3121b-e079-4b23-8ce2-5e28f1c683c0_1282x478.jpeg" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/Bd4hP5teiYNevDlI0sfdkfidxdaJsOnfsytse-g3se4=/aHR0cHM6Ly9zdWJzdGFja2Nkbi5jb20vaW1hZ2UvZmV0Y2gvd180MjQsY19saW1pdCxmX3dlYnAscV9hdXRvOmdvb2QsZmxfcHJvZ3Jlc3NpdmU6c3RlZXAvaHR0cHMlM0ElMkYlMkZzdWJzdGFjay1wb3N0LW1lZGlhLnMzLmFtYXpvbmF3cy5jb20lMkZwdWJsaWMlMkZpbWFnZXMlMkYwMGIzMTIxYi1lMDc5LTRiMjMtOGNlMi01ZTI4ZjFjNjgzYzBfMTI4Mng0NzguanBlZw== 424w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/PKtqOeWu6tkTXYTCsa90XBOm7CW- 848w, https://reader.miniflux. 1272w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/rOUwkDEs7Ag- 1456w" sizes="100vw"/><img src="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/-9iDfWncA6dHu3SO3-" alt="" srcset="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/0_7cZyQfAtWKbBTzqcJk-_ 424w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/JFxz7lOBEPRn9AKR4oq9bZY4ZWu9l-SGI2oqglTVCYg=/aHR0cHM6Ly9zdWJzdGFja2Nkbi5jb20vaW1hZ2UvZmV0Y2gvd184NDgsY19saW1pdCxmX2F1dG8scV9hdXRvOmdvb2QsZmxfcHJvZ3Jlc3NpdmU6c3RlZXAvaHR0cHMlM0ElMkYlMkZzdWJzdGFjay1wb3N0LW1lZGlhLnMzLmFtYXpvbmF3cy5jb20lMkZwdWJsaWMlMkZpbWFnZXMlMkYwMGIzMTIxYi1lMDc5LTRiMjMtOGNlMi01ZTI4ZjFjNjgzYzBfMTI4Mng0NzguanBlZw== 848w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/sge1- 1272w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/-9iDfWncA6dHu3SO3- 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"/></picture></a></figure><p>In other words, the systems are just blindly following the data, which, as Ren pointed out,  typically look like this<a id="footnote-anchor-1" href="#footnote-1">1</a>:</p><figure><a href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff6a5eb1d-8aa3-4b51-b2c7-2422ba78cfed_1690x880.png" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/jNI_KAgptBlTwwI0KXxyeA4f4KDWin1ccoYs-trCMXo=/aHR0cHM6Ly9zdWJzdGFja2Nkbi5jb20vaW1hZ2UvZmV0Y2gvd180MjQsY19saW1pdCxmX3dlYnAscV9hdXRvOmdvb2QsZmxfcHJvZ3Jlc3NpdmU6c3RlZXAvaHR0cHMlM0ElMkYlMkZzdWJzdGFjay1wb3N0LW1lZGlhLnMzLmFtYXpvbmF3cy5jb20lMkZwdWJsaWMlMkZpbWFnZXMlMkZmNmE1ZWIxZC04YWEzLTRiNTEtYjJjNy0yNDIyYmE3OGNmZWRfMTY5MHg4ODAucG5n 424w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/CDXlBPJal2-eaH- 848w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/A7kvc8pYofvJ3oUu3vqUqj9o2DJJOPUoWaYT-ABQzM8=/aHR0cHM6Ly9zdWJzdGFja2Nkbi5jb20vaW1hZ2UvZmV0Y2gvd18xMjcyLGNfbGltaXQsZl93ZWJwLHFfYXV0bzpnb29kLGZsX3Byb2dyZXNzaXZlOnN0ZWVwL2h0dHBzJTNBJTJGJTJGc3Vic3RhY2stcG9zdC1tZWRpYS5zMy5hbWF6b25hd3MuY29tJTJGcHVibGljJTJGaW1hZ2VzJTJGZjZhNWViMWQtOGFhMy00YjUxLWIyYzctMjQyMmJhNzhjZmVkXzE2OTB4ODgwLnBuZw== 1272w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/5c1P7FbHkaBEUJLe5XcSfuPxQTrVaNi_etFF6UrrWaQ=/aHR0cHM6Ly9zdWJzdGFja2Nkbi5jb20vaW1hZ2UvZmV0Y2gvd18xNDU2LGNfbGltaXQsZl93ZWJwLHFfYXV0bzpnb29kLGZsX3Byb2dyZXNzaXZlOnN0ZWVwL2h0dHBzJTNBJTJGJTJGc3Vic3RhY2stcG9zdC1tZWRpYS5zMy5hbWF6b25hd3MuY29tJTJGcHVibGljJTJGaW1hZ2VzJTJGZjZhNWViMWQtOGFhMy00YjUxLWIyYzctMjQyMmJhNzhjZmVkXzE2OTB4ODgwLnBuZw== 1456w" sizes="100vw"/><img src="https://reader.miniflux." alt="" srcset="https://reader.miniflux. 424w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/j95uv-5sBf5geD_Oq6cfqy5MCzr7_s1CLgiaMSK1uRU=/aHR0cHM6Ly9zdWJzdGFja2Nkbi5jb20vaW1hZ2UvZmV0Y2gvd184NDgsY19saW1pdCxmX2F1dG8scV9hdXRvOmdvb2QsZmxfcHJvZ3Jlc3NpdmU6c3RlZXAvaHR0cHMlM0ElMkYlMkZzdWJzdGFjay1wb3N0LW1lZGlhLnMzLmFtYXpvbmF3cy5jb20lMkZwdWJsaWMlMkZpbWFnZXMlMkZmNmE1ZWIxZC04YWEzLTRiNTEtYjJjNy0yNDIyYmE3OGNmZWRfMTY5MHg4ODAucG5n 848w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/iBXmhXRmWa8cLGTPevXoqBtilRlID94hGneZ_T5JJ8Q=/aHR0cHM6Ly9zdWJzdGFja2Nkbi5jb20vaW1hZ2UvZmV0Y2gvd18xMjcyLGNfbGltaXQsZl9hdXRvLHFfYXV0bzpnb29kLGZsX3Byb2dyZXNzaXZlOnN0ZWVwL2h0dHBzJTNBJTJGJTJGc3Vic3RhY2stcG9zdC1tZWRpYS5zMy5hbWF6b25hd3MuY29tJTJGcHVibGljJTJGaW1hZ2VzJTJGZjZhNWViMWQtOGFhMy00YjUxLWIyYzctMjQyMmJhNzhjZmVkXzE2OTB4ODgwLnBuZw== 1272w, https://reader.miniflux. 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"/></picture></a></figure><p>§</p><p>Blind fealty to the statistics of arbitrary data is not AGI. It’s a hack. And not one that we should want. </p><p>§</p><p>As I wrote on Twitter a couple years ago, we need to “<a href="https://x.com/garymarcus/status/1384173525368393736?s=61&amp;t=2voLMkhJf6P349CqztWSAQ" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">invent then a new breed of AI systems that mix an awareness of the past with values that represent the future that we aspire to. Our focus should be on figuring on how to build AI that can represent and reason about *values*,  rather than simply perpetuating past data</a>”. </p><p>Until we shift our focus, we will see the same problems, over and over again.</p><p></p><p><em><strong>Gary Marcus</strong> is not taken in by fancy graphics. He wants to see AI that is consistent with human values. Support this newsletter if you’d like to see the same.</em></p><p><a href="https://garymarcus.substack.com/subscribe?" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">Subscribe now</a></p><p><a href="https://garymarcus.substack.com/p/race-statistics-and-the-persistent?utm_source=substack&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_content=share&amp;action=share" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">Share</a></p><a id="footnote-1" href="#footnote-anchor-1">1</a><p>Odds are that there are some items like this in the training set, that in a brighter system might have helped</p><figure><a href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F26711f3e-cfe6-4d68-b561-8cdb0fe718ab_1200x1251.jpeg" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/3wAehFk-3T4fH5DlzH8Mkm_ 424w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/rdKOdtgm06zjScOSDlcV_ 848w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/0N7-dUfiN84V4Csyu4D_4SSS-VW_ 1272w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/HdhhFLnzKaEpNHmufbkW- 1456w" sizes="100vw"/><img src="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/DkVTm_LQiRVUztvU-T0MpMJUe5Gz7Ps0-cAoX8IAER8=/aHR0cHM6Ly9zdWJzdGFja2Nkbi5jb20vaW1hZ2UvZmV0Y2gvd18xNDU2LGNfbGltaXQsZl9hdXRvLHFfYXV0bzpnb29kLGZsX3Byb2dyZXNzaXZlOnN0ZWVwL2h0dHBzJTNBJTJGJTJGc3Vic3RhY2stcG9zdC1tZWRpYS5zMy5hbWF6b25hd3MuY29tJTJGcHVibGljJTJGaW1hZ2VzJTJGMjY3MTFmM2UtY2ZlNi00ZDY4LWI1NjEtOGNkYjBmZTcxOGFiXzEyMDB4MTI1MS5qcGVn" alt="" title="" srcset="https://reader.miniflux. 424w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/CC5Oo- 848w, https://reader.miniflux. 1272w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/DkVTm_LQiRVUztvU-T0MpMJUe5Gz7Ps0-cAoX8IAER8=/aHR0cHM6Ly9zdWJzdGFja2Nkbi5jb20vaW1hZ2UvZmV0Y2gvd18xNDU2LGNfbGltaXQsZl9hdXRvLHFfYXV0bzpnb29kLGZsX3Byb2dyZXNzaXZlOnN0ZWVwL2h0dHBzJTNBJTJGJTJGc3Vic3RhY2stcG9zdC1tZWRpYS5zMy5hbWF6b25hd3MuY29tJTJGcHVibGljJTJGaW1hZ2VzJTJGMjY3MTFmM2UtY2ZlNi00ZDY4LWI1NjEtOGNkYjBmZTcxOGFiXzEyMDB4MTI1MS5qcGVn 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"/></picture></a></figure><p>But the level of actual cognitive comprehension of here is low. The modest number of properly labeled examples is presumably swamped by all the billions of watch advertisements.</p><p></p>